text:
Arrival Hall, fl 1
Next to Paris Baguette, Toilet, and Belt 44

This is an elegant place to deal international traffic. Changi Airport itself is most beautiful Airport of world and all establishment are of super star standards. The best in world is seen in infrastructure. This ATM also excellent   example of this best in world.
Useful ATM at the airport. They might charge for using other bank cards.
Located at arrival hall near ground transport desk.
